text: Salaspils Parish () is an administrative unit of the Salaspils Municipality, Latvia. It was created in 2010 from the countryside territory of Salaspils town. At the beginning of 2014, the population of the parish was 5329. == Towns, villages and settlements of Salaspils parish == * Acone * Bunči * Saulkalne * Stopiņi == See also == * Dole Manor * Doles sala * Vecdole Castle == References == == External links == * Category:Parishes of Latvia Category:Salaspils Municipality
